{"tid":1722054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共輸到仆哂街本身心諗死得，望著你班岸鳩仔分化林鄭就笑到見牙唔見眼","createTime":"2019-11-14T21:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:31:50.000Z","uid":150842,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e0828d0a5f3ec1dddb87f40223cb046b10964743","tid":1722054,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:31:59.000Z","msg":"不割，但要解決以下問題，有問題就要屌醒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. Poly 班手足既態度</span></span><br />\n抗爭唔係玩唔係小朋友玩戰旗game，冇經驗就學中大點搞，虛心受教。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相信中大手足既決定，說好的兄弟爬山各有各做？</span></span><br />\n大家做法有分歧我理解，但要相信手足既智慧。有不滿既，落中大同佢地開會講清楚提出論據，唔好係度散播謠言話中大人不滿又講騎劫又剩。<br />\n<br />\n有問題，就要提出<br />\n有做錯，就要反省<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請重拾運動自我修正既能力，諗下鬧緊交既你地冇哂方向對唔對得住在天之靈既手足？對唔對住為場運動犧牲左咁多既手足？</span>"},{"pid":"d5890b61ad28eed612452aff89a228261c55c1f9","tid":1722054,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:32:22.000Z","msg":"推到大家都望到"},{"pid":"029685455adef1afba3176f011649251d68111e4","tid":1722054,"uid":277189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:33:14.000Z","msg":"推 不分化"},{"pid":"f0cb6bdc088d9b2353960283a851af17cb069add","tid":1722054,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:33:21.000Z","msg":"Ph"},{"pid":"eb6108574f014c997ba1d20b66bc38b2221070de","tid":1722054,"uid":139703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ed5123793762777054ed79e7c673f788fdf97f","tid":1722054,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:34:01.000Z","msg":"問題係而家記招都開埋，就算大家拗完知道個開一條路換區選呢個決定可能有錯都好，咁可以點收返個決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852042a53d85693e586ce3035c793cc6ee14cace","tid":1722054,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:34:14.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n解決為上<br />\n屌手足撚齋屌唔俾建議既<br />\n一律都係分化撚"},{"pid":"fe2129d1a2540c48f168193090f32ce0d2678cc4","tid":1722054,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:34:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c92919fec346a2c33d903dde7f4de62a5f356091","tid":1722054,"uid":325181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:34:22.000Z","msg":"推唔到都推呀"},{"pid":"8e829e085cdc66345ed1fb07914cd07759121254","tid":1722054,"uid":169646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:35:08.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n成N個post屌緊暴大<br />\n就算要討論, 一個post都夠"},{"pid":"592a8ccf8b3a4d71c6cc0a28c7d55f12f0f34827","tid":1722054,"uid":147664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:35:20.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a8177e0b6ea19a2a2907265b3f253fcfe4f98bfa","tid":1722054,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:35:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">澄明思諸，勿陷分化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n捉鬼係永遠捉唔完，中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面<br />\n<br />\n平心而論，對家要收風根本唔會帶住支槍，帶得支槍入去理大就擺明預咗比你捉，達成佢地分化你地嘅政治目的，既然有鬼會帶住支槍，冇槍嘅鬼都肯定會有，正如連登夠有五毛、TG各公海都一定會有對家臥底，呢個係common sense，所以我再重覆一次，<span style=\"color: red;\">中共黨史上最叻就係滲透同分化，大家要默認永遠總有隻鬼喺左近，點捉都捉唔曬，過度緊張捉鬼反而會陷入分化局面</span>"},{"pid":"1acb1929b31531ba04272fcb75217a5a838f3ced","tid":1722054,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:36:51.000Z","msg":"幫我推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1f1377ac2368d8b5bdf4a001cf023a36e61879","tid":1722054,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ed5123793762777054ed79e7c673f788fdf97f","tid":1722054,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:34:01.000Z","msg":"問題係而家記招都開埋，就算大家拗完知道個開一條路換區選呢個決定可能有錯都好，咁可以點收返個決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:38:15.000Z","msg":"記招開左係不可逆既事<br />\n但開行車線都係24小時既事，可能之後都有變數，可以趁deadline 未到前入去同手足傾傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471cb2ddd307a99025bb197f9d73ea6e05f3edf5","tid":1722054,"uid":52339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:38:23.000Z","msg":"甴近平呀！"},{"pid":"75f4010b88643b5dca64d6ebafb6a98355f9bc26","tid":1722054,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:38:23.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n有咩問題出黎<br />\n我地集體幫手解決<br />\n推到旭日行動大成功為止"},{"pid":"e950d6e7afb673216b28bc80953e5117a704e6e0","tid":1722054,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:38:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27a655cd1b9c968201f3d002122fd2dad1c47d88","tid":1722054,"uid":258571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cbdd75db19e3ed1043918cde6770f2f286b74c8","tid":1722054,"uid":78762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:40:59.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"94ee3d265629e4a13dd66f2c3cec96e26ff2c5e8","tid":1722054,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:41:27.000Z","msg":"不分化<br />\n<br />\n唔駛特登捉內鬼 但都要觀察每個人<br />\n<br />\n發現自己情緒有問題 就去冷靜左先<br />\n<br />\n件事已經係事實 只需諗點團結應對<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有錯可以提醒 不必怪責</span></span>"},{"pid":"afdf59b3688ee009da55dd61fb7c931cedaf6102","tid":1722054,"uid":8938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:41:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nbe humble好重要"},{"pid":"fdbeb10af9098c0268f9631f8be61b71700c5d94","tid":1722054,"uid":152809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:43:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n有咩問題就講出嚟 大家一齊解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e60cd013925c00914a23e9a026d8e5afd36bf4","tid":1722054,"uid":159569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:54:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cc5425c61021db3bcf51d7e129eaf3ef3502604","tid":1722054,"uid":150842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:55:53.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c37d09a3d9043c7b500d7017638d7fce6929585d","tid":1722054,"uid":121676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T22:01:32.000Z","msg":"我認為大學係要守住<br />\n<br />\n但投擲雜物既地點可以再選擇<br />\n<br />\n亦有好多唔同既地點可以投擲<br />\n<br />\n咁啲狗就冇左攻入大學既理由"}]}